'''西田斯特拉特福德城'''（Westfield Stratford City）<ref name="Facts">{{cite web | url=http://uk.westfield.com/stratfordcityleasing/news/press-toolkit/ | title=Press Toolkit | publisher=uk.westfield.com | accessdate=2011-09-07 | archive-date=2011-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110924210447/http://uk.westfield.com/stratfordcityleasing/news/press-toolkit/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>是位於[[倫敦|倫敦]][[史特拉福_(倫敦)|史特拉福]]的一個購物中心，開幕於2011年9月13日<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/standard/article-23941806-launch-date-announced-for-mega-mall-near-olympic-park.do | title=Launch date announced for Mega Mall | publisher=thisisLondon | accessdate=2011-09-07 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110421010539/http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/standard/article-23941806-launch-date-announced-for-mega-mall-near-olympic-park.do | archivedate=2011年4月21日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=//uk.westfield.com/stratfordcityleasing/news/press-releases/westfield-stratford-city-to-open-in-150-days | title=Westfield Stratford City: Opening date | publisher=uk.westfield.com | accessdate=2011-04-16 | archive-date=2011-10-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111005062500/http://uk.westfield.com/stratfordcityleasing/news/press-releases/westfield-stratford-city-to-open-in-150-days/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，總面積達 {{convert|1905542|sqft|sqm}}<ref name="size">{{cite web | url=http://www.westfield.com/corporate/property-portfolio/united-kingdom/stratfordcity.html | title=Westfield Group Property Portfolio: Stratford City Overview | publisher=Westfield UK | access-date=2011-09-14 | url-status=dead | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111019162841/http://www.westfield.com/corporate/property-portfolio/united-kingdom/stratfordcity.html | archive-date=2011-10-19 }}</ref>，是歐洲規模最大的都會型購物中心之一，也是英國規模第三大的購物中心，僅次於都市中心和特拉福德中心。西田斯特拉特福德城由[[西田集團|西田集團]]開發所有。

